            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Google combines IP address, device GPS, account history, and query language (e.g. adding "near me"). Signed-in users on Android give the strongest location signal; anonymous desktop users rely on IP.</p></div></div>
